data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED. Offer deadline of 4.17.2024 at 4PM. Stop the CAR! The one you've been waiting for is now available! This home has been lovingly & carefully maintained- the definition of move-in-ready PERFECTION! From the moment you enter, you'll be wowed by how pristine this home is. The gleaming hardwoods welcome you at the front door & continue throughout the main floor. The front room has tasteful built-in shelving, & has ample room to function as a home office/library. The natural light floods in, filling the the 10 foot ceilings with radiant beams. The spacious family room has a gas fireplace (with brand new logs!) which creates cozy ambiance in the colder months & cooler evenings. The kitchen has an attached breakfast nook that looks out & connects to your maintenance-free deck. The kitchen is a baker & chef's dream with large island, SS appliances, an abundance of counter space, & LOADS of storage. The smart mirrored doors on the pantry create an open & airy feeling. Dining Area can also function as pet area, homework nook, or overflow eating space. Main Floor Laundry is ideal for multi-taskers! On the second floor you'll find the spacious Primary Suite complete with your own personal built-in vanity area. Fall in love with the huge walk-in closet that is steps away from the attached full bath- which is another light-flooded space that is sure to delight. 2 more bedrooms & full bath round out the 2nd floor. The basement has tall ceilings w/ daylight windows- making it cheery & bright. Convenient work area is adjacent to the living room & full bath. The 4th bedroom has large windows & nice-sized closet. Ample storage areas! Updates include New Carpet (2024), HVAC (2016), Roof (2013) See complete list in docs! Community clubhouse & pool are just a stone's throw away. This neighborhood offers more than a home- but a lifestyle! With convenient access to freeways & shopping, you'll find convenient amenities without the crazy hustle & bustle of some suburban areas.
